 "_finding": "The demo/stream_driver.py epoch sequence, byte-checked: the rev-3 streaming-driver design (advance -> assert -> drain per epoch; heartbeats = empty-fact advances driving expiry). One double_spike alert from the two hot sensor-1 readings 2s apart; the later hot reading at t=11000 finds its would-be partners long expired and stays silent. The demo's WAL-replay determinism claim rides on exactly this sequence being oracle-identical."
